            "title": "中國｜重慶原副市長江敦濤等3官員被雙開",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中國｜重慶原副市長江敦濤等3官員被雙開\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國｜重慶原副市長<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"江敦濤\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:江敦濤;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/江敦濤\">江敦濤</a>等3官員被雙開</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中央紀委國家監委今日發布3份通報，宣布3名部級或以上官員被「雙開」處分，包括重慶市政府原副市長江敦濤、湖南人大常委會原黨組書記烏蘭，以及國家煙草專賣局原副局長韓占武。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">江敦濤政績觀嚴重偏差 急功近利</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中央紀指江敦濤喪失理想信念，背棄初心使命，政績觀嚴重偏差，急功近利、對抗組織審查，廉潔底線失守，違規收受禮品、禮金，違規贈送禮金，利用職務影響為他人謀取私利，紀法底線失守，利用職務便利為他人在工程承攬、規劃審批、項目建設等方面謀利，並非法收受巨額財物，決定予以開除黨籍及開除公職處分。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3a11ab0b-335b-3654-aedb-8930838aecb3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">烏蘭背棄初心使命 結交政治騙子</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經查，烏蘭喪失理想信念，背棄初心使命，搞政治投機，結交政治騙子；接受可能影響公正執行公務的宴請；違規收受禮品、禮金；家風不正，對家人失管失教；目無法紀，毫無敬畏，利用職務便利為他人在企業經營、項目承攬等方面謀利，並非法收受巨額財物，決定予以開除黨籍及開除公職處分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓占武廉潔底線失守 搞權色交易</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓占武被指喪失理想信念，背棄初心使命，違反中央八項規定精神，違規收受禮品、消費卡；違反組織原則，不按規定報告個人有關事項，違規為他人在幹部職工錄用方面謀取利益並收受財物；廉潔底線失守，搞權色、錢色交易；大肆收錢斂財，利用職務便利為他人在企業經營等方面謀利，被予以開除黨籍及開除公職處分。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%AF%E5%B8%82%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E6%95%A6%E6%BF%A4%E7%AD%893%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E9%9B%99%E9%96%8B-052715042.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-13 13:42:01",
